{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/v-center-server-for-windows-to-v-center-server-appliance","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"vcenter-server-for-windows-vs-vcenter-server-appliance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vcenter-server-for-windows-vs-vcenter-server-appliance\" aria-label=\"vcenter server for windows vs vcenter server appliance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vCenter Server for Windows vs vCenter Server Appliance?</h1>\n<p>VMware의 vCenter는 두가지 버전이 있다. vCenter Server for Windows는 윈도우 위에서 애플리케이션으로 돌릴 수 있는 시스템이며, vCenter Server Appliance는 vCenter기반의 vCenter 운용을 위한 시스템이다. 간략한 특징을 정리해보면</p>\n<h3 id=\"vcenter-server-for-windows\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vcenter-server-for-windows\" aria-label=\"vcenter server for windows permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vCenter Server for Windows</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>6.7을 마지막으로 flffl</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"vcenter-server-appliance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vcenter-server-appliance\" aria-label=\"vcenter server appliance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>vCenter Server Appliance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>리눅스 위에서 돌아감</li>\n<li>-</li>\n</ul>\n<p>전자는 애플리케이션 셋이고 후자는 OS+애플리케이션 셋이라는 차이점이 있으며, </p>\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"참조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"참조 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참조</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Migrating vCenter Server for Windows to vCenter Server Appliance : <a href=\"https://docs.vmware.com/en/VMware-vSphere/6.5/com.vmware.vsphere.upgrade.doc/GUID-9A117817-B78D-4BBE-A957-982C734F7C5F.html\">https://docs.vmware.com/en/VMware-vSphere/6.5/com.vmware.vsphere.upgrade.doc/GUID-9A117817-B78D-4BBE-A957-982C734F7C5F.html</a></li>\n<li>Farewell, vCenter Server for Windows : <a href=\"https://blogs.vmware.com/vsphere/2017/08/farewell-vcenter-server-windows.html\">https://blogs.vmware.com/vsphere/2017/08/farewell-vcenter-server-windows.html</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://aerocode.net\">https://aero